### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱشْتَرَوُا۟ ٱلضَّلَـٰلَةَ بِٱلْهُدَىٰ فَمَا رَبِحَت تِّجَـٰرَتُهُمْ وَمَا كَانُوا۟ مُهْتَدِينَ</span>

### English

They are the ones who trade guidance for misguidance. But this trade is profitless, and they are not ˹rightly˺ guided.